title: Colonels Resign
new-page: true 
subtitle: Colonels disagreements with our policies have grown too severe.
tags: event
view-if: colonels_dissent >= 60 and pilsudski_dead = 1
on-arrival: colonels_strength *= 0.3; robotnicy_bbwr -= 5; n_advisors -= 1 if slawek_advisor == 1; n_advisors -= 1 if prystor_advisor == 1; colonels_resigned = 1
max-visits: 1

= Colonels leaders resign

Our policy choices have greatly offended the Colonels faction. Many of our most experienced leaders have resigned.
